'''Multiple gender attraction''' ('''MGA'''), sometimes '''multi-gender attraction''', is an [[umbrella term]] that includes any [[Romance (love)|romantic]] or [[sexual orientation]] which experiences attraction to more than one [[gender]]. Such orientations include, but are not limited to, [[bisexuality]], [[pansexuality]], and [[polysexuality]].

